<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">分组凑整法，是几个数连乘时，先把5的倍数与2的倍数结组相乘，再用积与其他因数相乘，这样计算积不变。如果几个因数分别为a、b、c、d、e，其中a=5m，d=2n根据乘法的交换律和结合律，可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a×b×c×d×e=(a×d)×b×c×e</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算。</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">19×12×25=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">19×12×25</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=19×(12×25)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=19×300</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=5700</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>